long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Feel the adrenaline of the McLaren P1 with a thrilling live wallpaper that brings this high-performance supercar to your Chrome new tab.

The McLaren P1 Live Wallpaper highlights the futuristic design and incredible speed of this iconic car. Every new tab immerses you in the world of speed and precision.

Features:
McLaren P1 Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension enhances your experience with a stunning chrome wallpaper and practical tools. As one of the best chrome live wallpapers, it turns your chrome background into a showcase of luxury and performance.

For more exciting live wallpapers, visit Gameograf.com. Explore extensions like: Ferrari LaFerrari Live Wallpaper, Lamborghini Aventador Live Wallpaper, Porsche 911 GT Live Wallpaper, Aston Martin Valkyrie Live Wallpaper, Bugatti Divo Live Wallpaper.
